并不能禁止通过 sudo su -进行切换。</description></item><item><title>mihomo warp 配置教程</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/mihomo-warp-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/mihomo-warp-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</guid><description>chmod +x /usr/local/bin/mihomo</description></item><item><title>openssh</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/openssh/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/openssh/</guid><description>在大多数基于 Linux 的操作系统中，OpenSSH 都已经预安装。如果没有可以使用系统的包管理器进行安装。</description></item><item><title>oracle cloud console connection</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/oracle-cloud-console-connection/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/oracle-cloud-console-connection/</guid><description>本指南介绍如何通过控制台连接到 Oracle Cloud 实例，涵盖三种连接方法用于系统恢复和 BIOS 访问。</description></item><item><title>oracle cloud netboot reinstall</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/oracle-cloud-netboot-reinstall/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/oracle-cloud-netboot-reinstall/</guid><description>本指南介绍如何使用 netboot 恢复损坏的 Oracle Cloud VPS 实例，支持 AMD 和 ARM 架构重新安装系统。</description></item><item><title>starship pastel powerline 预设</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/starship-pastel-powerline-%E9%A2%84%E8%AE%BE/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/starship-pastel-powerline-%E9%A2%84%E8%AE%BE/</guid><description>此预设的灵感来自于 M365Princess。 它同时也演示了 Starship 的路径替换功能。</description></item><item><title>starship pastel powerline整理文档</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/starship-pastel-powerline%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/starship-pastel-powerline%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3/</guid><description>本文根据 Starship 官方 Pastel Powerline 预设页面整理，补充了可直接使用的命令和配置，适合直接套用到本机 starship 环境。</description></item><item><title>tcping 与udping 使用</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/tcping-%E4%B8%8Eudping-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/tcping-%E4%B8%8Eudping-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</guid><description>本指南介绍三种常用的网络连通性测试工具：ping、tcping 和 udping，适用于常规 ICMP 测试、TCP 端口连通性测试、以及 UDP 端口连通性测试。</description></item><item><title>tea in the snow 个人 zsh 配置整理</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/tea-in-the-snow-%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA-zsh-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/tea-in-the-snow-%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA-zsh-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86/</guid><description>仓库地址：https://github.com/tea-in-the-snow/terminal-configuration/blob/main/zsh/zshrc</description></item><item><title>vps常用脚本</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/vps%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/vps%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/</guid><description>支持Windows 10、Windows 11、Windows Server 2012 R2、Windows Server 2016、Windows Server 2019、Windows Server 2022</description></item><item><title>zsh optimization guide</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/zsh-optimization-guide/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/zsh-optimization-guide/</guid><description>很多人从 Oh My Zsh（OMZ）入坑 Zsh，它开箱即用、功能丰富、文档齐全，但加载大量插件后会出现明显的启动延迟，甚至打开终端需要等1~2秒才能输入命令。</description></item><item><title>zsh安装和美化指南</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/zsh%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/zsh%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description>这份文档基于当前机器上的 ~/.zshrc 与 ~/.zshaliases 整理，目标是从零安装并复现一套兼顾颜值和效率的 zsh 环境。</description></item><item><title>zsh部署与bash配置迁移指南</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/zsh%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%8Ebash%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%BF%81%E7%A7%BB%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/zsh%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%8Ebash%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%BF%81%E7%A7%BB%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description>如果你已经习惯了 bash，但想切换到 zsh，最稳妥的方式不是“直接覆盖旧配置”，而是先安装 zsh，再把 bash 中真正有用的配置逐步迁移过去。</description></item><item><title>备份方案</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%BD%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%BD%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</guid><description>本文介绍如何在 Linux 服务器上创建一个受限的备份用户，并使用 rclone 工具定期将 /etc、/var/www 和 /opt 三个目录备份至远程服务器。内容涵盖用户权限控制、SSH 公钥登录、rclone 配置及定时任务设置。</description></item><item><title>创建新用户并启用ssh登录</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E6%96%B0%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%B9%B6%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8ssh%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E6%96%B0%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%B9%B6%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8ssh%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95/</guid><description>首先创建一个名为 rclone-backup 的用户，并为其设置密码：</description></item><item><title>zsh与zinit启动时间测试方法</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/zsh%E4%B8%8Ezinit%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/zsh%E4%B8%8Ezinit%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</guid><description>目标只有一件事：先测量，再定位，再做对照实验。</description></item><item><title>oracle cloud netboot recovery</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/oracle-cloud-netboot-recovery/</link><pubDate>Tue, 20 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/oracle-cloud-netboot-recovery/</guid><description>本教程介绍如何通过 netboot.xyz 在 Oracle Cloud 实例上进行网络安装系统，解决 DD 脚本失败且无法使用 VNC 访问的情况。</description></item><item><title>syncthing 同步方案</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/syncthing-%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/syncthing-%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</guid><description>因为旧电脑突然故障，我的部分重要数据被丢失（没养成备份数据的习惯！！！）。因此我需要备份windows上的重要数据。选来选去，我最终选择syncthing 。</description></item><item><title>waf</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/waf/</link><pubDate>Sat, 03 May 2025 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/waf/</guid><description>Published:2025年5月3日 | at 06:36 | 浏览: 207</description></item><item><title>ssh方案 winscp putty</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/ssh%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88-winscp-putty/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/ssh%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88-winscp-putty/</guid><description>在使用多个ssh客户端以后，我决定选择winscp+putty的方案。在这个方案里，winscp主要用于sftp和管理多个ssh节点。</description></item><item><title>debian11升级debian12</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/debian11%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7debian12/</link><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/debian11%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7debian12/</guid><description>本文将指导如何升级 Debian 11 Bullseye 到 Debian 12 Bookworm。</description></item><item><title>wsl</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/wsl/</link><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/wsl/</guid><description>浏览: 3,044 次浏览 作者: 去年夏天 分类: 发布时间: 2023-10-31 11:49</description></item><item><title>syncthing linux步神器</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/syncthing-linux%E6%AD%A5%E7%A5%9E%E5%99%A8/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Mar 2023 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/syncthing-linux%E6%AD%A5%E7%A5%9E%E5%99%A8/</guid><description>自从在学校和家里都放上了NAS之后，由于网络的问题，从学校远程访问家中/从家中远程访问学校总会遇到速度的限制。迫于无奈，使用文件同步来实时同步两台NAS上的文件，不仅起到加速访问的功能，还能够保证数据的异地备份。</description></item><item><title>acme</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/acme/</link><pubDate>Thu, 03 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/acme/</guid><description>本文将介绍使用 acme.sh 配置自动续签的 SSL 证书。</description></item><item><title>cloudflare warp 教程</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/cloudflare-warp-%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Feb 2021 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/cloudflare-warp-%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</guid><description>原文链接: https://p3terx.com/archives/use-cloudflare-warp-to-add-extra-ipv4-or-ipv6-network-support-to-vps-servers-for-free.html</description></item><item><title>debian11开机操作</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/debian11%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Apr 2018 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/ops/debian11%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/</guid><description>apt-get install bash-completion</description></item></channel></rss>